<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tirumaṭantaiyu <supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yamaṭantaiyun tiruppuyaṅkaḷi <unclear>li</unclear>ṉitiruppa Irunilamu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>m perumai yeyta Eṇṭicaiyuṅ kuṭai niḻaṟṟa maṉṉava rellām vantiṟaiñca marapil
<lb n="3"/>vanta maṇimuṭi cūṭit teṉkumariyum vaṭakaṅkaiyun tiraikkaṭale yellaiyākap pār muḻutuṅ kayalāṇai parantu ce
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṅkoluṭaṉ vaḷara maṉṉiya vira<hi rend="grantha">siṁ hāsa</hi> ṉattu Ulakamuḻutuṭaiyāroṭum viṟṟiruntaruḷi māmutal matikkulam viḷa 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kkiya komutaṟ koccaṭaiyava<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi> rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">trabhva</hi> naccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">l</hi> la<hi rend="grantha">bhade</hi> vaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="18"><g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num> vatu kiḻkaḷak
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">l</hi> la<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi> cca<note n="311-1">This inscription is left unfinished.</note>
